        <h1 className="text-4xl font-extrabold text-center text-indigo-700 mb-2 tracking-tight">SafePost üåü</h1>
        <p className="text-center text-sm text-gray-500 mb-8">Predict how safely your followers will react to your post.</p>

        <label className="border-2 border-dashed border-gray-300 rounded-xl p-5 w-full text-center cursor-pointer hover:border-indigo-400 transition block">
